# Pizza API

## To use these HTTP  endpoint install the REST Client plugin in VSCode.

GET https://pizza-api.projectcodex.net/api/pizzas

### Create a cart

GET https://pizza-api.projectcodex.net/api/pizza-cart/create?username=AmoMandy


### Get a cart

GET https://pizza-api.projectcodex.net/api/pizza-cart/rTPVoApZHz/get

### Add a pizza to the cart

POST https://pizza-api.projectcodex.net/api/pizza-cart/add
content-type: application/json

{
    "cart_code" : "rTPVoApZHz",
    "pizza_id" : 9
}

